*[http://www.ldstoday.com/ LDS Today] - News related to The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints
*[http://search.ldslibrary.com/ LDS Library] - Full text search engine; more than 3,300 important LDS books. 
*[http://www.mormonwiki.com Mormon wiki] - Wiki for and supported by Latter-day Saints
*[http://ldsfaq.byu.edu/ LDSFAQ at byu.edu] - A comprehensive index answering many common questions. Uses large portions of The Encyclopedia of Mormonism
*[http://www.mormonmomma.com Mormon Momma] - scholarship and fellowship for LDS women
*[http://www.ldsaudio.com/free-book-of-mormon/ Audio Book of Mormon] - free download, mp3 format
*[http://www.GrupoSUD.com GrupoSUD.com] - A large general interest Spanish-language discussion group for LDS Church members.
*[http://www.theldswoman.com The LDS Woman] - Free online social network and magazine for LDS women.
====Music====
* [http://www.lds.org/churchmusic/ Church Music] - official website
* [http://www.mormontabernaclechoir.org/ Mormon Tabernacle Choir] - official website
* [http://www.musicandthespokenword.com/ Music and the Spoken Word] - official website
* [http://www.suvchoir.org/ Saints Unified Voices]
* [http://www.hymnwiki.org/ HymnWiki] - a wiki for hymns, with a large focus on LDS content (hymns of all faiths are welcome).
* [http://www.liahona.net/ Liahona.net] - free LDS-type music in MP3 format.

===Criticism of the Mormon Church===
*[http://www.carm.org/mormon.htm CARM.ORG] - Most popular Christian aplogetics website

===Academic forums===
<!-- PLEASE read the discussion page before adding to these or editing these. -->
