*[http://www.fairlds.org FAIR] - Foundation for Apologetic Information & Research
*[http://www.dialoguejournal.com Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought] - An independent quarterly covering history, religion, science and social issues. 
*[http://www.mhahome.org/ The Mormon History Association]
* [http://www.pbs.org/mormons/ The Mormons] - Frontline + American Experience four hour PBS documentary aired April 30-May 1, 2007

